VThe gene pool of Haiti is about 95.5% Sub-Saharan African, 4.3% European, with the rest showing some traces of East Asian genes; according to a 2010 autosomal genealogical DNA testing. The same study found that Jamaica\u2019s gene pool is 78.3% Sub-Saharan African, 16.0% European, and 5.7% East Asian.
